# UI test - Roku developer

![alt text](data:image/png;base64,)


Layout of HomePage of the test for Zemoga, made up with;
 - `HTML5`
 - `CSS3`
 - `[Bootstrap](https://getbootstrap.com/)`
 
Additionally I implement `"Lato" font` from [Google Fonts](https://fonts.google.com/)  and some `media queries`(different from the provided by boostrap) to make more dynamic the content in phones.

Based in the reference provided by the Zemoga the result is a responsive webpage that fit with the layout requirements:
